Class FilterExpression

java.lang.Object
  com.threerings.honeybird.FilterExpression
All Implemented Interfaces:
Filter
public class FilterExpression
extends Object
implements Filter

Filters a specific source using a fixed operator and restriction. These are created automatically by using a function that creates a Filter on a metric or a dimension.

and

public Filter and(Filter additional)
Description copied from interface: Filter
Combines this filter with the given filter and restricts results such that both must accept an item to include it. This has a lower precedence than Filter.or(com.threerings.honeybird.Filter) if an or is also included in a filter.

or

public Filter or(Filter additional)
Description copied from interface: Filter
Combines this filter with the given filter and allows an item through if either accepts it. This has a higher precedence than Filter.and(com.threerings.honeybird.Filter) if an and is also included in a filter.
